197
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:22,000
Salima, lihat. Itu stasiunnya.

198
00:16:46,680 --> 00:16:47,920
Detonator!

199
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:51,600
Pak Polisi!

200
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:53,200
Prasad berhasil!

201
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:00,840
Keretanya sudah dekat!

202
00:17:13,520 --> 00:17:14,720
Hei, berhenti!

203
00:17:15,960 --> 00:17:18,280
Berhenti! Rem!

204
00:17:30,040 --> 00:17:32,000
Kereta datang, <i>Abbu</i>.

205
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:36,440
<i>Penumpang Kereta Ekspres Gorakhpur,
tetap di dalam!</i>

206
00:17:37,080 --> 00:17:38,040
Di sini berbahaya.

207
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:40,240
<i>Jangan turun!</i>

